Package circuitbuilder

circuitbuilder is the main package for the CircuitBuilder software
Author:
elliot gorman
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    And
    The 'and' logic gate.
    ButtonsPanel
    The custom JPanel which houses all the gate buttons.
    CircuitBuilder
    The main class, builds and launches the GUI.
    DrawingPanel
    The DrawingPanel custom JPanel, acts as a canvas for the user to drop logic gates and connections onto.
    FullAdder
    The 'fulladder' logic gate.
    HalfAdder
    The 'halfadder' logic "gate".
    Input
    The Input class extends the Logic Gate IO class and serves as the input pin on the gates.
    Led
    The 'led' gate, allows the user to see the output.
    Link
    The 'link' class, establishes a connection from input to output.
    LogicGate
    The 'template' that all logic gates extend.
    LogicGateIO
    abstract 'template' for the connectingInput and connectingOutput classes.
    Nand
    The 'nand' logic gate.
    Nor
    The not-or ('nor') logic gate.
    Not
    The 'not' logicGate.
    Or
    The 'or' logic gate.
    Output
    The 'output' class, for sending values over.
    Switch
    The 'switch' class, the source of input.
    Xnor
    The 'xnor' logic gate.
    Xor
    The 'xor' logic gate.
